/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/uwerx_p5_25_124/final_report.md:33:On transfers to `uniswapPoolAddress`, `_transfer` first removes the full `amount` from the sender and credits the recipient with that full `amount`, then separately calls `_burn(from, burnAmount)`. The sender therefore needs enough balance for `amount + burnAmount`, not just `amount`.
